    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This prologue to the world of Ämäränth marks (hopefully) the beginning of a long journey through the noosphere and beyond.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In corde nostro somniamus de divino rerum tumultu</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ämäränth: The Last Day of My Adolescence is a short (1-2h) and simple visual novel. There are no sprites for the characters, but you can unlock little secrets as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I developed this game in my spare time to bring to life a universe I've been building up for several years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm aware that the result is (clearly) amateurish and (very) rough around the edges, but I hope to pique your interest even if only for a brief moment!</p>",
